## slots.txt - Pre-configured tunnel addresses
## Place this file next to setup.bat
## Format: hostname|token (one per line)
## Lines starting with ## are ignored by the script
##
## Example:
## rdp1.example.com|eyJhIjoiYjkyNWM5NTkwZGQ0...
## rdp2.example.com|eyJhIjoiYzEyM2Q0NTY3ODkw...
## office-pc.example.com|eyJhIjoiZGVmMTIzNDU2...
